address: SVP Road, Rangampet Rd, Warangal, Telangana 506001, India
hotelDescription:
On the NH3 road, this casual hotel is a 16-minute walk from the lakefront Bhadrakali Temple, 5 km from Warangal train station and 6 km from Warangal Fort.
 The unpretentious rooms have Wi-Fi, TVs and minibars; suites add sitting areas. Family rooms sleep up to 5 guests. Room service is available 24/7.
 There's a colourful international restaurant. A breakfast buffet and parking are available.

hotelDescription:
Amid shops and restaurants lining National Highway 163, this down-to-earth hotel is 18 minutes' walk from the Kakatiya Zoological Park and 3 km from the 12th-century Thousand Pillar Temple.
 The casual, simply furnished rooms come with Wi-Fi access and TVs. Some add sitting areas. Room service is offered.
 Amenities include an informal restaurant, as well as a coffee shop. Event space is available.
